<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الَّذِينَ غَلَبُوا}</span> ... أَصْحَابُ النُّفُوذِ فِيهِمْ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
